## Module 2: Water as a Shared Resource 

<img src="https://images.code.org/7d77c6874cfc72b89c3038a424cb768f-image-1435686009471.gif" style="float: left; margin-right: 20px;" width="200px"/>In this Earth Science module, students will investigate the importance of ground water and the impacts of water usage on aquifer levels as well as exploring the modeling of important parts of the water cycle including evaporation and infiltration of water into different types of soils to recharge the aquifers.

